ct_hdst     <- sp_hdst[selected_x5,]
ct_5x       <- sp_5x[selected_x5,]

cut_funcs <- function(x,brk=c(1,3,5)){
    cutx <- cut(x,breaks=c(0,brk[-length(brk)],max(brk[length(brk)],x)+1),right=F)
    return(as.numeric(cutx))
}

ct_hdst_cut <- apply(ct_hdst,1,cut_funcs)
ct_5x_cut   <- apply(ct_5x,1,cut_funcs)

ct_hdst_rel <- apply(ct_hdst_cut,2,relative_func)
ct_5x_rel   <- apply(ct_5x_cut,2,relative_func)

pltdat_hdst  <- cbind.data.frame(loc_hdst[,1:2],ct_hdst_rel)
pltdat_5x  <- cbind.data.frame(loc_5x[,1:2],ct_5x_rel)

colnames(pltdat_hdst) <- c("x","y",paste0(selected_x5,"_HDST"))
colnames(pltdat_5x) <- c("x","y",paste0(selected_x5,"_5X"))
